pageProduct.name: Swisse Calm And Sleep Gummies 60 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Calm + Sleep Gummies are a deliciously convenient way to get a targeted dose of nutrients to support a healthy stress response, decrease nervous tension and relax the nervous system to reduce restless sleep*. These 99% sugar free gummies are packed full of flavour, contain no artificial sweeteners and are formulated with:

Vitamin B5 to assist the body in coping with stress and support a healthy stress response.

*Passionflower, traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to decrese nervous tension, relax the nervous system, calm the nerves and encourage restful sleep.

Size: 60 Pack

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. This medicine contains 2.73g maltitol per maximum recommended daily dose and may have a laxative effect or cause diarrhoea. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

Vitamin B5 (pantothenic acid from calcium pantothenate) 750 micrograms; Passionflower (passiflora incarnata extract 32.9 mg) equiv. dry herb 125 mg; Ashwagandha (withania somnifera extract 1.25 mg) equiv. dry root 125 mg.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Chew 2 gummies an hour or two before bed, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat.
